; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">,</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-45\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.165em; margin: 0px; font-style: italic;\">b</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-46\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px;\">≤</span><span style=\"vertical-align: 0px;\">10</span><sup>9</sup><span style=\"vertical-align: 0px;\">)<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;гурван бүхэл тоо өгөгдөнө.</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.600000381469727px; font-style: italic; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">r</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;нь улаан,</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.600000381469727px; font-style: italic; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">g</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;нь ногоон,</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.600000381469727px; font-style: italic; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">b</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;нь цэнхэр цэцэгний тоо.</span></span></p>\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Фокс Сиалын хийж чадах хамгийн олон цэцгийн баглааны тоо.</span></span></p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Input 1:</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">3 6 9</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> <strong>Output 1:</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">6</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 